{"Id":497930,"Title":"北山堂诗","Dynasty":"明","Author":"林弼","Context":"瞻彼北山，其下有堂。堂有甘旨，吾亲是将。胡为乎来，于钟之阜。钟有北山，匪我之旧。我思北山，思之永叹。庭有长椿，堂有丛萱。椿之茂矣，萱之秀矣。悠悠我思，曷云觏止。有图有诗，莫慰我思。北山之归，我心则夷。自古在昔，以忠为孝。勖尔世良，是则是效。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"b75e06ec6f2e707890da5316d5d715ba","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":6835112,"Sentence":"瞻彼北山，其下有堂。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhān bi běi shān ，jī xià yǒu táng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835113,"Sentence":"堂有甘旨，吾亲是将。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"táng yǒu gān zhi ，wú qīn shì jiāng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835114,"Sentence":"胡为乎来，于钟之阜。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hú wéi hū lái ，yú zhōng zhī fù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835115,"Sentence":"钟有北山，匪我之旧。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"zhōng yǒu běi shān ，fěi wǒ zhī jìu ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835116,"Sentence":"我思北山，思之永叹。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ sāi běi shān ，sāi zhī yǒng tàn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835117,"Sentence":"庭有长椿，堂有丛萱。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tǐng yǒu cháng chūn ，táng yǒu cóng xuān ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835118,"Sentence":"椿之茂矣，萱之秀矣。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chūn zhī mào yi ，xuān zhī xìu yi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835119,"Sentence":"悠悠我思，曷云觏止。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yōu yōu wǒ sāi ，hé yún gòu zhi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835120,"Sentence":"有图有诗，莫慰我思。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yǒu tú yǒu shī ，mò wèi wǒ sāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":6835121,"Sentence":"北山之归，我心则夷。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":n